
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge"/>
  <title>Event Decline</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f2f3f7;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #e74c3c;
      font-size: 22px;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .event-details {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 15px;
      background-color: #fdfdfd;
      border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .event-details p {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .event-details ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .event-details li {
      font-size: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .contact-organizer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      background-color: #fff3f3;
      border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 13px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <h1>Hi {{userName}},</h1>
    <p>
      We regret to inform you that you have not been selected to participate in the event
      <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong>.
    </p>

    <div class="event-details">
      <p>ðŸ“… Event Details:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Event Name:</strong> {{eventTitle}}</li>
        <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{eventDate}}</li>
        <li><strong>Strat Time:</strong> {{eventStartTime}}</li>
        <li><strong>Organizer:</strong> {{organizerName}}</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

   <div class="contact-organizer">
  If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to the organizer <strong>{{organizerName}}</strong> using the chat button provided in the event portal.
</div>


    <p>
      We truly appreciate your interest and encourage you to stay connected for future opportunities.
    </p>

    <p>Best regards,<br />The Event Management Team</p>
  </div>

    <div class="footer">
    <p>The Event Management Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
